* Granularity\n(Grain)
** Definition
***_ Level of detail per row
***_ What each row represents
** Fact Table Grain
***_ Determined by combination of dimension keys
***_ "One row per order line item"
** Dimension Table Grain
***_ One row per entity (current state)
***_ One row per entity per version (SCD Type 2)
***_ One row per entity per time period
** Critical Rule
***_ Once aggregated, detail is lost forever
***_ Always document grain explicitly
@endmindmap
